message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and information extraction. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper uses machine learning techniques, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as it deals with extracting information from text, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it uses deep learning models, and "cs.DB" (Databases) as it deals with extending a knowledge base.
